1
00:02:10,341 --> 00:02:12,016
Zeyi

2
00:02:16,408 --> 00:02:17,855
I've been looking for you for the whole night

3
00:02:18,055 --> 00:02:20,662
Zhu Xuan told me you are here

4
00:02:20,862 --> 00:02:22,410
Why are you still in the studio

5
00:02:22,610 --> 00:02:26,198
Tomorrow is the deadline of ideal scripts

6
00:02:26,398 --> 00:02:28,804
I'm here to finish that

7
00:02:29,004 --> 00:02:30,374
Fell asleep accidentally

8
00:02:30,574 --> 00:02:31,949
Thank you

9
00:02:35,137 --> 00:02:36,430
Not smooth?

10
00:02:36,630 --> 00:02:39,463
It's difficult for art students to find a job

11
00:02:39,663 --> 00:02:42,307
Especially when I do it on my own

12
00:02:42,507 --> 00:02:49,040
The demand of that art club is too high
I can't get in

13
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:54,059
I don't think you will be beaten by these difficulties

14
00:02:58,941 --> 00:03:00,143
It's late at night

15
00:03:00,343 --> 00:03:03,189
I will go back to the domitory

16
00:03:03,389 --> 00:03:07,250
Go to sleep

17
00:03:11,657 --> 00:03:17,657
Bye

18
00:03:37,367 --> 00:03:41,125
Ye Zi has been busy lately
Don't know when she can arrive

19
00:03:41,325 --> 00:03:45,426
Ye Zi

20
00:03:45,626 --> 00:03:46,406
You are back

21
00:03:47,974 --> 00:03:50,013
I told you she would come back

22
00:03:50,213 --> 00:03:53,152
It seems that you know her better than me

23
00:03:53,352 --> 00:03:54,435
It's true

24
00:03:54,635 --> 00:03:56,980
Do you know her favorite song and favorite food

25
00:03:57,180 --> 00:03:59,577
Stop arguing
Let's start eating

26
00:03:59,777 --> 00:04:01,274
Let me do it

27
00:04:03,126 --> 00:04:05,588
You still like arguing with each other after several months

28
00:04:05,788 --> 00:04:09,087
She likes to argue with me

29
00:04:09,287 --> 00:04:11,288
Ye Zi,you tell me

30
00:04:11,488 --> 00:04:12,575
I'm starving
Let's eat

31
00:04:12,775 --> 00:04:14,886
soup

32
00:04:15,086 --> 00:04:16,182
Wait for a moment

33
00:04:19,344 --> 00:04:22,235
Ye Zi,you look skinny

34
00:04:22,435 --> 00:04:23,462
Really

35
00:04:23,662 --> 00:04:24,162
Right

36
00:04:24,300 --> 00:04:25,368
Not good?

37
00:04:25,568 --> 00:04:27,150
Of course not

38
00:04:27,350 --> 00:04:29,226
How can you be more skinny than me

39
00:04:29,426 --> 00:04:32,274
I'm the most beautiful in the universe

40
00:04:34,009 --> 00:04:34,554
Ye Zi

41
00:04:34,754 --> 00:04:36,972
How's your intern in the magazine office

42
00:04:38,730 --> 00:04:41,602
Just to serve the editors
and learn nothing

43
00:04:43,253 --> 00:04:48,062
I thought you may be appreciated
since you were the only one picked for this intern

44
00:04:48,262 --> 00:04:49,941
Like a waitress

45
00:04:50,141 --> 00:04:53,933
Don't worry
They will be regretted

46
00:04:54,133 --> 00:04:54,633
Right

47
00:04:54,754 --> 00:04:57,711
They will beg for your works
because you are so brilliant

48
00:04:59,429 --> 00:05:01,215
It's rare to see you two agree on the same point

49
00:05:02,769 --> 00:05:04,821
We are about to graduate

50
00:05:05,021 --> 00:05:06,012
What's your plan

51
00:05:06,212 --> 00:05:13,402
I have feelings for this place
and I will find a job here

52
00:05:15,552 --> 00:05:16,728
No problem

53
00:05:16,928 --> 00:05:20,140
Two hours from your home to here

54
00:05:20,340 --> 00:05:24,803
What's your plan,Liu

55
00:05:27,732 --> 00:05:29,092
Why are you looking at me

56
00:05:29,292 --> 00:05:33,083
I won't leave you either

57
00:05:33,283 --> 00:05:35,650
Then we four can be together again

58
00:05:35,850 --> 00:05:38,403
You will feel lonely without me

59
00:05:38,603 --> 00:05:40,771
Maybe a little bit

60
00:05:42,334 --> 00:05:50,349
You don't want to leave us or Daniao

61
00:05:50,549 --> 00:05:52,654
That's settled

62
00:05:52,854 --> 00:05:54,853
Maybe we can work together one day

63
00:05:55,053 --> 00:05:57,275
Cheers for our future

64
00:05:57,475 --> 00:06:00,108
Hope that we all can fufill our dreams

65
00:06:00,308 --> 00:06:01,605
Right

66
00:06:01,805 --> 00:06:02,756
Cheers

67
00:06:05,922 --> 00:06:07,248
Ye Zi,don't drink too much

68
00:06:07,448 --> 00:06:08,973
Not much

69
00:06:10,979 --> 00:06:12,464
You are different now

70
00:06:12,664 --> 00:06:15,508
Maybe you are the one to get drunk first

71
00:06:15,708 --> 00:06:21,022
OK,let's get drunk tonight

72
00:06:21,222 --> 00:06:23,760
Cheers

73
00:06:46,894 --> 00:06:48,388
Ye Zi

74
00:06:48,588 --> 00:06:49,883
Let me ask you one thing

75
00:06:53,996 --> 00:06:56,669
Do you still miss Xiang Zeyi

76
00:07:15,711 --> 00:07:20,220
If I tell you no,it's a lie

77
00:07:20,420 --> 00:07:23,859
He's my first love after all

78
00:07:24,059 --> 00:07:30,984
We will truly grow up after tonight

79
00:07:31,184 --> 00:07:33,903
Xiang Zeyi

80
00:07:37,341 --> 00:07:40,351
He's just part of my college life

81
00:07:40,551 --> 00:07:44,514
Just memory

82
00:07:47,497 --> 00:07:49,710
OK

83
00:07:49,910 --> 00:07:51,108
I don't worry any more

84
00:07:51,308 --> 00:07:53,551
You know me

85
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:57,040
I will not be obessed with one issue
Don't worry

86
00:07:57,300 --> 00:08:00,000
that's good

87
00:08:00,980 --> 00:08:02,200
We will be good

88
00:09:59,268 --> 00:10:02,112
When I earn millions a year,
we get married

89
00:10:02,312 --> 00:10:03,206
Pardon

90
00:10:03,406 --> 00:10:04,608
We get married

91
00:10:04,808 --> 00:10:05,730
Pardon

92
00:10:05,930 --> 00:10:07,349
Get married

93
00:10:12,765 --> 00:10:15,349
If you like,I can draw for you everyday

94
00:10:15,549 --> 00:10:17,848
When I graduate

95
00:10:18,048 --> 00:10:20,101
I will collect the whole box of it

96
00:10:23,527 --> 00:10:27,771
It means it's not my iPod
You can't give it back to me

97
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:32,580
You're mine

98
00:12:08,300 --> 00:12:10,300
Promisses

99
00:12:24,620 --> 00:12:31,500
What is promise

100
00:14:14,117 --> 00:14:15,825
As long as this painting exists,

101
00:14:16,025 --> 00:14:17,383
I will be with you

102
00:14:36,235 --> 00:14:37,405
Ye Zi

103
00:14:48,420 --> 00:14:49,096
Ye Zi

104
00:14:51,357 --> 00:14:52,375
Where were you

105
00:14:52,575 --> 00:14:53,777
I've been looking for you

106
00:14:53,977 --> 00:14:56,548
I walked around

107
00:14:56,748 --> 00:14:59,097
Don't know when I will come back

108
00:14:59,297 --> 00:15:01,424
Idiot

109
00:15:01,624 --> 00:15:03,575
If you want to come here,
I can be with you at any time

110
00:15:05,771 --> 00:15:06,568
Ye Zi,Zhu Xuan

111
00:15:08,259 --> 00:15:09,741
Let's take a photo together

112
00:15:09,941 --> 00:15:13,103
Right,it seems that we never take a picture together

113
00:15:13,303 --> 00:15:14,461
OK,let's take a photo

114
00:15:14,661 --> 00:15:16,367
Who can help us

115
00:15:16,567 --> 00:15:18,821
We can take selfie by your phone

116
00:15:21,041 --> 00:15:22,573
Monitor

117
00:15:22,773 --> 00:15:23,741
Use mine

118
00:15:23,941 --> 00:15:25,602
Right,use hers

119
00:15:27,941 --> 00:15:28,681
OK

120
00:15:29,939 --> 00:15:32,937
Are you ready

121
00:15:33,137 --> 00:15:35,875
Three two one

122
00:16:05,852 --> 00:16:07,797
Sorry,Ye Zi

123
00:16:08,053 --> 00:16:09,073
There was a meeting

124
00:16:09,273 --> 00:16:09,983
Sit down please

125
00:16:10,183 --> 00:16:11,273
Sit

126
00:16:11,473 --> 00:16:13,211
I just arrived

127
00:16:15,134 --> 00:16:17,543
Do you have any problems

128
00:16:17,743 --> 00:16:19,693
I'm here to thank you

129
00:16:19,893 --> 00:16:21,349
Thanks for you trust

130
00:16:21,549 --> 00:16:25,574
You shouldn't thank me most

131
00:16:25,774 --> 00:16:27,561
Director Shao,you really like joking

132
00:16:27,761 --> 00:16:29,043
I'm serious

133
00:16:29,243 --> 00:16:34,685
You should thank the chief painter of this program most

134
00:16:34,885 --> 00:16:39,514
He knows your works best

135
00:16:39,714 --> 00:16:43,321
As you say so,I wish I could see him

136
00:16:45,639 --> 00:16:49,741
He will be back soon

137
00:16:49,941 --> 00:16:50,732
OK

138
00:16:50,932 --> 00:16:52,521
Director Shao

139
00:16:52,721 --> 00:16:54,737
Come in

140
00:17:04,947 --> 00:17:06,355
Let me introduce him to you

141
00:17:06,555 --> 00:17:10,776
This is the chief painter
Mr.Xiang Hui

142
00:17:13,405 --> 00:17:15,181
-This one
-No need to introduce

143
00:17:19,709 --> 00:17:24,690
You two need time for dicussion

144
00:17:24,890 --> 00:17:26,214
I won't bother you

145
00:17:54,113 --> 00:17:55,513
Xiang Hui

146
00:18:06,844 --> 00:18:11,009
Nice to meet you,Mr.Xiang Hui
My name is Ye Zi

147
00:18:16,848 --> 00:18:20,887
Do you intend to embarrass your partner like this

148
00:18:42,223 --> 00:18:44,270
Ye Zi,hope we have a good cooperation

149
00:18:44,470 --> 00:18:45,946
Hope so

150
00:18:50,202 --> 00:18:54,053
It's late at night
We can discuss this later when we are both available

151
00:19:03,610 --> 00:19:04,993
See you later

152
00:19:05,193 --> 00:19:06,166
Mr.Xiang Hui

153
00:19:44,017 --> 00:19:46,463
So we are coopeating with Xiang Zeyi?

154
00:19:46,663 --> 00:19:47,947
Xiang Hui

155
00:19:50,552 --> 00:19:51,902
When did he change the name

156
00:19:55,783 --> 00:19:56,569
Here you are

157
00:19:56,769 --> 00:19:58,743
Wu Kai told me you are here

158
00:20:00,587 --> 00:20:04,683
I'm thinking maybe we should talk to Xinran

159
00:20:07,829 --> 00:20:09,804
What to talk

160
00:20:10,004 --> 00:20:11,885
Xinyu's gone

161
00:20:12,085 --> 00:20:13,254
Zhu Xuan

162
00:20:13,454 --> 00:20:15,396
I want to help her

163
00:20:15,596 --> 00:20:20,447
I think we should help her get out of that pain

164
00:20:20,647 --> 00:20:24,622
Help her lick her wounds?

165
00:20:24,822 --> 00:20:25,885
Why are you saying this

166
00:20:26,085 --> 00:20:29,509
All of us are upset about this

167
00:20:29,709 --> 00:20:31,906
Xi

168
00:20:33,530 --> 00:20:42,263
I remember that you once told me we should care about somebody in an accepted way

169
00:20:42,463 --> 00:20:50,449
But there's nothing we can do
about Xinru's leaving

170
00:20:50,649 --> 00:20:57,564
What Liu needs most is to let out all her feelings
No one can help her right now

171
00:20:57,764 --> 00:21:01,425
We shouldn't bother her

172
00:21:01,625 --> 00:21:03,207
Leaving her alone

173
00:21:03,407 --> 00:21:05,412
Is how we care about her

174
00:21:14,202 --> 00:21:15,273
Xi

175
00:21:15,473 --> 00:21:23,254
Zhu Zi is also upset about Xinyu's leaving
even more grieve than Xinran

176
00:21:23,454 --> 00:21:27,814
Leave her alone

177
00:22:16,373 --> 00:22:17,897
She may not come

178
00:22:18,097 --> 00:22:19,194
She will

179
00:22:40,264 --> 00:22:40,976
Xinran

180
00:22:46,992 --> 00:22:47,803
Come on

181
00:22:58,967 --> 00:23:00,017
Eat more

182
00:23:06,457 --> 00:23:08,730
Come on,Xinran
I'll drink with you

183
00:23:08,930 --> 00:23:10,649
Me,too

184
00:23:12,972 --> 00:23:14,066
Come on

185
00:23:14,266 --> 00:23:15,886
Cheers

186
00:23:28,400 --> 00:23:31,220
There's good news

187
00:23:31,420 --> 00:23:34,900
Ye Zi sold her comics

188
00:23:35,100 --> 00:23:36,612
You can rest assured

189
00:23:36,812 --> 00:23:38,456
That's good

190
00:23:38,656 --> 00:23:39,928
Xinran

191
00:23:40,128 --> 00:23:42,464
My collection of essays is about to publish

192
00:23:42,664 --> 00:23:43,679
I'll send you one

193
00:23:43,879 --> 00:23:45,108
You must read it

194
00:23:45,308 --> 00:23:51,820
In the following days,I and Zhu Zi will become busy
You two must help us

195
00:23:52,020 --> 00:23:53,931
Of course

196
00:23:54,131 --> 00:23:56,059
We do this all the time

197
00:23:56,259 --> 00:23:57,236
Right,Xinran

198
00:23:57,436 --> 00:23:59,285
Come on

199
00:24:02,892 --> 00:24:04,839
Eat more

200
00:24:05,039 --> 00:24:06,431
Come on

201
00:24:16,589 --> 00:24:22,135
This is Xinyu's

202
00:24:39,719 --> 00:24:43,058
I'm fine
Don't blame Zhu Xuan

203
00:24:43,258 --> 00:24:45,482
I'm sorry

204
00:24:54,212 --> 00:24:56,150
Drink one glass

205
00:24:56,350 --> 00:24:58,326
OK

206
00:25:09,848 --> 00:25:13,412
Never see you obey like this

207
00:25:26,849 --> 00:25:28,565
Xinyu was like you

208
00:25:31,061 --> 00:25:34,622
She hardly ever listened to me

209
00:25:46,669 --> 00:25:50,223
Xinran,it's past

210
00:25:50,423 --> 00:25:53,154
There's no pain in heaven

211
00:25:53,354 --> 00:25:55,847
Xinyu will be happy there

212
00:26:02,189 --> 00:26:04,172
She's ten younger than me

213
00:26:04,372 --> 00:26:08,339
The year she was born was cold

214
00:26:10,579 --> 00:26:13,062
I remember my mom asked me to hold her

215
00:26:13,262 --> 00:26:19,348
She looked so tiny and soft

216
00:26:19,548 --> 00:26:21,172
How did I dare to hold her

217
00:26:23,375 --> 00:26:28,185
But the minute I got close to her,
she smiled to me

218
00:26:30,280 --> 00:26:36,934
I seemed to forget how cold that winter was
when I saw her smile

219
00:26:39,848 --> 00:26:42,028
The year I got into high school

220
00:26:42,228 --> 00:26:45,458
The school put up our names on the walls

221
00:26:45,658 --> 00:26:49,498
She ebled herself in the crowd

222
00:26:49,698 --> 00:26:51,118
She didn't even know many characters

223
00:26:51,318 --> 00:26:54,473
But she tried so hard to find my name

224
00:26:56,973 --> 00:27:00,485
After she found it

225
00:27:00,685 --> 00:27:07,418
she removed my name from that paper at night

226
00:27:07,618 --> 00:27:09,676
and said it was a gift to me

227
00:27:11,985 --> 00:27:16,770
When I was in high school,
I was not allowed to go home at night

228
00:27:16,970 --> 00:27:23,320
She took the meal made by mom
and wait for me outside the school

229
00:27:23,540 --> 00:27:31,720
She shouted at me
"sister,your meal"

230
00:27:36,040 --> 00:27:37,120
She was only six then

231
00:27:39,780 --> 00:27:44,460
She asked me if there's bad guy in school

232
00:27:44,460 --> 00:27:49,660
when she watched me eating

233
00:27:50,926 --> 00:27:57,813
She asked me if there's anyone bullying me

234
00:27:58,013 --> 00:28:00,515
If there is

235
00:28:00,715 --> 00:28:02,436
you can tell me

236
00:28:02,636 --> 00:28:05,022
I will help you

237
00:28:10,325 --> 00:28:12,466
Don't worry

238
00:28:13,263 --> 00:28:14,642
I will protect you

239
00:28:38,262 --> 00:28:39,422
I thought

240
00:28:39,622 --> 00:28:44,061
Every problem will be solved after we grow up

241
00:28:47,953 --> 00:28:49,249
Now I know

242
00:28:49,449 --> 00:28:56,701
Problems occur after we grown up

243
00:29:48,829 --> 00:29:50,266
Waiter,a glass of lemonade

244
00:29:50,466 --> 00:29:53,309
You should drink wine

245
00:29:53,509 --> 00:29:56,386
If I get drunk,who send you home

246
00:29:56,586 --> 00:30:01,269
You can drink as much as you want
I will be with you

247
00:30:02,775 --> 00:30:04,665
You are really my good brother

248
00:30:07,294 --> 00:30:11,730
It's no use drinking to get away with sadness

249
00:30:13,472 --> 00:30:15,270
It's better to say it out

250
00:30:15,470 --> 00:30:17,569
Don't you know

251
00:30:17,769 --> 00:30:20,946
Don't say that

252
00:30:21,670 --> 00:30:25,784
It will be a disaster if it's heard by my wife

253
00:30:27,590 --> 00:30:28,090
OK

254
00:30:30,863 --> 00:30:33,511
Just joking

255
00:30:36,872 --> 00:30:38,010
It's for Ye Zi?

256
00:30:39,919 --> 00:30:41,650
For Zhu Xuan

257
00:30:54,702 --> 00:30:57,539
I'm in love with Ye Zi for 15 years

258
00:30:57,739 --> 00:30:59,258
Do you know that

259
00:30:59,458 --> 00:31:02,414
I know you are in love with Ye Zi

260
00:31:02,614 --> 00:31:05,142
But I don't know for so long

261
00:31:07,823 --> 00:31:13,710
In these 15 years,I only love her

262
00:31:13,910 --> 00:31:20,108
Actually Ye Zi will see your love to her one day

263
00:31:20,308 --> 00:31:21,274
She saw

264
00:31:21,474 --> 00:31:22,864
She just pretends not to know

265
00:31:26,658 --> 00:31:28,909
You know it clearly

266
00:31:29,109 --> 00:31:31,368
You can not ask for it

267
00:31:34,175 --> 00:31:36,319
Don't want to give up so easily

268
00:31:36,519 --> 00:31:38,199
Come on

269
00:31:50,085 --> 00:31:54,678
Zhang Daniao is nothing

270
00:31:54,878 --> 00:31:57,496
He thinks himself as something

271
00:31:59,876 --> 00:32:01,663
He's nothing

272
00:32:03,305 --> 00:32:04,504
Listen,Xi

273
00:32:06,057 --> 00:32:07,862
Zhang Daniao

274
00:32:09,682 --> 00:32:11,910
He's not what you see

275
00:32:15,088 --> 00:32:16,454
What is he like

276
00:32:16,654 --> 00:32:21,748
He's not responsible

277
00:32:27,422 --> 00:32:30,678
He only knows to play computer games

278
00:32:30,878 --> 00:32:32,421
He doesn't know how to earn money

279
00:32:32,621 --> 00:32:34,592
Right

280
00:32:34,792 --> 00:32:36,886
He lets you suffer

281
00:32:40,935 --> 00:32:42,323
Xinran is drunk

282
00:32:42,523 --> 00:32:44,713
Go pick her up with me

283
00:32:47,922 --> 00:32:49,389
Go with me

284
00:32:49,589 --> 00:32:52,696
I don't dare to go alone

285
00:32:56,464 --> 00:32:58,049
Xiang Zeyi

286
00:32:58,249 --> 00:33:00,005
Ye Zi is there
Are you sure you don't want to go

287
00:33:12,343 --> 00:33:14,844
What's next

288
00:33:16,726 --> 00:33:19,009
No next

289
00:33:19,209 --> 00:33:22,336
Wait for her response

290
00:33:24,505 --> 00:33:26,951
No matter what the result will be

291
00:33:27,151 --> 00:33:29,816
I try one more time

292
00:33:33,018 --> 00:33:34,808
I support you

293
00:33:40,845 --> 00:33:43,746
Actually we both know the result

294
00:33:43,946 --> 00:33:48,761
As your brother,I support you to chase her back

295
00:33:55,508 --> 00:33:57,264
Good luck to you

296
00:33:57,464 --> 00:33:58,859
Good luck to me

297
00:34:07,025 --> 00:34:08,228
One more glass

298
00:34:34,188 --> 00:34:35,673
Daniao

299
00:34:37,096 --> 00:34:39,848
Xinran,see
Daniao is here

300
00:34:51,058 --> 00:34:53,172
Xixi,let's go home

301
00:34:53,372 --> 00:34:55,247
Go

302
00:35:00,173 --> 00:35:02,758
Let's go home

303
00:35:02,958 --> 00:35:04,363
Hurry up

304
00:35:23,542 --> 00:35:25,174
Xinran,let's go home

305
00:36:26,007 --> 00:36:27,882
Mr.Xiang Hui

306
00:36:28,082 --> 00:36:33,318
You look like one of my old friends in college

307
00:36:37,420 --> 00:36:40,380
But he's braver than you

308
00:36:43,520 --> 00:36:47,660
and he's careful

309
00:36:47,856 --> 00:36:49,804
Gentle

310
00:36:50,004 --> 00:36:53,313
And he has a sense of humor

311
00:36:57,820 --> 00:37:00,580
He likes to touch my hair

312
00:37:03,120 --> 00:37:06,060
He always prepared surprise for me

313
00:37:10,120 --> 00:37:13,540
and made many promises

314
00:37:18,260 --> 00:37:19,300
But

315
00:37:29,500 --> 00:37:32,080
He went missing one day

316
00:37:35,480 --> 00:37:37,500
He disappeared

317
00:37:45,280 --> 00:37:48,160
Maybe he's dead

318
00:38:12,560 --> 00:38:14,940
Don't say anything

319
00:38:29,540 --> 00:38:35,140
Just give me a second

320
00:39:38,180 --> 00:39:39,220
Thank you

321
00:39:41,980 --> 00:39:43,180
Mr.Xiang Hui

322
00:40:48,120 --> 00:40:49,040
Are you okay

323
00:40:58,380 --> 00:40:59,080
Xinran

324
00:41:00,760 --> 00:41:05,120
Do you remember I said I will fulfill one of you wishes

325
00:41:05,306 --> 00:41:08,749
If you want to,you can make this wish at any time

326
00:41:08,949 --> 00:41:15,915
I'm always the star for you

327
00:41:16,115 --> 00:41:18,336
I'll be with you

328
00:41:18,560 --> 00:41:20,800
Wait for you to make this wish

329
00:41:33,380 --> 00:41:36,260
I'm sorry
This is my fault
